{"questionId":"22027","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Hank sets up a bird table in his garden to provide the local birds with some food. Hank notices&nbsp;that a specific bird, a large magpie, visits several times per month and he names him Bill. Hank&nbsp;models the number of times per month that Bill visits his garden as a Poisson distribution with&nbsp;mean <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>3</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>1</mn></math>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Over the course of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>3</mn></math> consecutive months, find the probability that Bill visits the garden:</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>on exactly <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>12</mn></math> occasions.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>X</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>~</mo><mtext>Po</mtext><mfenced><mrow><mn>3</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mtext>Po</mtext><mfenced><mrow><mn>9</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></mfenced></math><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em>(M1)</em></strong></p>\n<p><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mtext>P</mtext><mfenced><mrow><msub><mi>X</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>12</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>0799</mn><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mfenced><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>0798950</mn><mo>…</mo></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em>A1</em></strong></p>\n<p><br><em><strong>[2 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"22027","referenceCode":"21M.2.AHL.TZ2.5b.i","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"on exactly 12 occasions.","paper":"2","level":"HL","questionNumber":"b.i","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 2]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 4—Statistics and probability","Topic 4—Statistics and probability","AHL 4.17—Poisson distribution"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}